<div class="col">
  <h1 class="welcome-header-title">Welcome to CryptoStrikers!</h1>
  <p class="welcome-header-text">To get started, please enter your email address and choose a nickname.</p>
  <br>
  <p class="welcome-header-text">When you hit Submit, you will be asked to sign a message identifying you as the owner of your wallet address. This will secure your account.</p>
  <br>
  <p class="welcome-header-text">Note: Your email address and nickname are stored on CryptoStrikers' servers and not on the blockchain. You can delete your account at any time.</p>
  {{#if referrer}}
    <div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
      <h5 class="alert-heading">You have been invited by <span>{{referrer.nickname}}</span>.</h5>
      <hr>
      {{#if (lt referralPacksClaimed 5000)}}
        <p class="mb-0">Sign up below, buy a pack, and your second one is on us!</p>
        <p class="mb-0">Free packs remaining: <span>{{sub 5000 referralPacksClaimed}}/5000</span></p>
      {{/if}}
      <p class="mb-0">Once you buy a pack, you can join our Referral Program to start earning exclusive cards.</p>
    </div>
  {{/if}}
</div>
